## DEC-001 — (example) Ledgers are markdown, not a database

- **Category:** architecture
- **Date:** {{TODAY}}
- **Decision:** Institutional memory lives in git-versioned markdown read
  start-to-finish, not in a queryable store.
- **Why:** the value is provenance and non-relitigation for a human reader;
  similarity-recall of facts is a different primitive (kernel memory /
  module.ingest). Ordered human-readable history beats query here.
